Package io.pet.violation

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IViolation
    This is the IViolation interface, it defines the methods to be implemented by subclass defining the checking of a violation, like PET violation.

    AbstractViolation

    ParallelViolation
    This is the ParallelViolation class.
    Reconstruction
    This is the Reconstruction class, it defines function in order to check if a secret from any type of secret sharing is in the end reconstructed, i.e. if the the task with the reconstruction stereotypes receive the exact numbers of shares or computation shares that it needs
    SSViolation
    This is the SSViolation class, it defines functions in order to detect secret sharing, additive secret sharing and function secret sharing violation
